Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,志温姐 玄关的包裹是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,早上保管的 万年小姐的包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,万年小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,住二层的 得赶快送去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但是炸鸡块…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:31.84,Default - up,,0,0,0,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那我帮你送去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,花名送去? 没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.18,0:00:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,之前还那么怕生 花名长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,志温姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,按了门铃后该说什么教教我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,尽可能仔细详密地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,花名…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:41.30,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(331.486,624.657)}{\fad(900,900)\c&H009C54D4\bord2\blur1}Step4 「二楼的会员大会」
